{"tid":1321330,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我而家宣布 7/21改去九龍塘集會 同意請入黎比趣！","createTime":"2019-07-15T15:39:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T16:15:30.000Z","uid":167938,"like":7,"dislike":77,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d22bf38764d04ffa8ad6675b3f45de443be99106","tid":1321330,"uid":167938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:39:57.000Z","msg":"1。九龍塘係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">獅子山下既象徵</span></span><br />\n上一次代唔會唔認同<br />\n2。九龍塘有花墟道球場及窩打老道  絕對容納到超多人<br />\n3。有地鐵/火車/巴士/小巴 係香港<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">真正</span>心臟地帶<br />\n<br />\n4。有錢居民，狗唔夠膽亂黎<br />\n5。行去旺角/樂富/深水埗都輕鬆 <br />\n6。有兩間大學加兩大宿舍同教堂可以避難<br />\n7。又一城出口多<br />\n8。地勢有高有低 難於被追擊 包抄 增加包圍所需狗力<br />\n<br />\n第128點細佬我諗<br />\n其他係隔離post度見到有位巴打講 借左黎加入<br />\n歡迎任屌 熱烈討論<br />\n<br />\n屌我好啦唔好屌老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9d385e6fb41176dae4188bb364869178c292f7b","tid":1321330,"uid":167938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:40:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7930141c4bdbdd9fcbf9a3c4c7d8a16ea0fe88aa","tid":1321330,"uid":167938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:40:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a087506741a05ee1e2ef28b990b8c93464ed8ecc","tid":1321330,"uid":167938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:41:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"416499e028b77fea28995414aa4a780a5d6301c0","tid":1321330,"uid":167938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:41:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1f4931670ba86ff9cc8bbe4aad6cad47d6c3a39c","tid":1321330,"uid":167938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:41:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"87809433fad29dcbe073363a989e0577e6d3d481","tid":1321330,"uid":167938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:41:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1676a4c56d12c13b3772528ff4e60580ed935732","tid":1321330,"uid":167938,"like